OL,3,CMan arrested after elderly woman dies
OL,4,Cduring a trip to shops
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after an
OL,7,Felderly pedestrian died in a car crash
OL,8,Fin Liverpool.
OL,10,FMargaret Perry, 81, was seriously
OL,11,Finjured and died in hospital following
OL,12,Fthe collision on Longmoor Lane near
OL,13,Fthe junction of Third Avenue,
OL,14,FFazakerley on Friday (5 December).
OL,16,FHer family is being supported by
OL,17,Fspecialist police officers as the
OL,18,Finvestigation continues.
