OL,3,CMan arrested after elderly woman dies
OL,4,Cduring a trip to shops
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Chris Saidi
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with
OL,8,FMargaret's family as they continue to
OL,9,Fgrieve this tragic loss.
OL,11,F"Our priority is to ensure that we get
OL,12,Fanswers for Margaret's family."
OL,14,FPolice were called to the scene at
OL,15,F4.15pm and were searching for a dark-
OL,16,Fcoloured car, which did not stop after
OL,17,Fthe incident.
