OL,3,CMan arrested after elderly woman dies
OL,4,Cduring a trip to shops
OL,6,FOfficers are continuing to appeal to
OL,7,Fanyone who has CCTV or doorbell
OL,8,Ffootage that captured the incident to
OL,9,Fcome forward and said they are
OL,10,Fparticularly interested in talking to
OL,11,Fany motorists who were in the area who
OL,12,Fmay have dashcam footage of the
OL,13,Fincident.
OL,15,FA 69-year-old man from Fazakerley has
OL,16,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of causing
OL,17,Fdeath by dangerous driving and failing
OL,18,Fto stop.
OL,20,FHe remains in police custody.
