OL,4,Cduring a trip to shops
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Saidi added, "Although
OL,7,Fsomeone has now been arrested, we
OL,8,Fcontinue to appeal for anyone with
OL,9,Finformation to come forward.
OL,11,F"Any help we receive, no matter how
OL,12,Finsignificant it may seem may help."
OL,14,FAnyone who witnessed the collision or
OL,15,Fcaptured anything on CCTV or dashcam
OL,16,Fis asked to contact the serious
OL,17,Fcollision investigation unit at
OL,18,FMerseyside Police on 0151 777 5747, or
OL,19,Femail SCIU@merseyside.police.uk
OL,20,Fquoting 0620 of December 5.
